ources including the display, speakers, microphone, user inputs, steering wheel controls, instrument cluster and sensors.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc16-723-developing-carplay-systems-part-2","kind":"article","type":"topic"}}}